From 2ccdc738d7cf9524582f1babaa879b1efd19df80 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Karl-Erik Gustafsson <ke.gustafsson@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Apr 2026 23:22:42 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Claude/replace mdns libraries 7k tvp (#72)

* refactor(mdns): replace dnssd2 and mdns-js with @astronautlabs/mdns

Consolidates advertising and discovery onto a single pure-TypeScript
mDNS/DNS-SD implementation with no native dependencies. The previous
optional native `mdns` fallback is no longer needed.

* fix(mdns): strip trailing .local from configured hostname

@astronautlabs/mdns appends the mDNS TLD (".local") to the hostname
internally, so a configured external hostname already ending in ".local"
(from EXTERNALHOST, proxy_host, or settings.hostname) would be
advertised as "host.local.local" and make the SRV target unresolvable.
Normalize by stripping a trailing dot and a trailing ".local" before
passing the value to Advertisement.
