From 2ea380273afd09e60c812af3386df2159737bedc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: KE Gustafsson <ke.gustafsson@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 21 Apr 2026 22:13:44 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] fix(mdns): suppress non-fatal EADDRINUSE startup noise

Patch @astronautlabs/mdns before Browser/Advertisement load so
its bind-time addMembership EADDRINUSE log is suppressed.

Keep other membership errors visible and add tests that reset the
helper module cache so the patch test is isolated from prior loads.
Per-file commit comments:

src/mdnsPatch.ts (line 1): add a narrow patch for @astronautlabs/mdns that filters only bind-time EADDRINUSE membership noise and restores console.error afterward.
src/mdns.js (line 20): apply the mDNS patch before loading Advertisement so startup advertising avoids the misleading upstream log.
src/discovery.js (line 17): apply the same mDNS patch before loading Browser so discovery uses the patched bind path too.
test/mdnsPatch.ts (line 1): add tests that suppress only EADDRINUSE, preserve other errors, and clear the helper module cache to avoid cross-test state leakage.
